            <img data-src="" style="opacity: 0; width: 335px !important; height: 313.641px !important;" title="background4.png" class="img_loading" data-ratio="0.9362416107382551" data-w="596" data-type="png" _width="100%" src="static/img/adv/background4.png"></section><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="line-height: inherit; white-space: pre-wrap; color: #FFFFFF; font-size: 14px; font-family: 站酷高端黑; background-color: #80B135;">贴心服务</span></p></section></section></section><section class="" data-tools="135编辑器" data-id="86412" style="border: 0px none; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 1em auto; border: none; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="border-left-width: 3px; border-left-style: solid; border-left-color: rgb(170, 166, 149); box-sizing: border-box;"><section class="" style="margin-left: 2px; padding: 0.6em; line-height: 1.5; text-align: left; border-left-style: solid; border-left-width: 1px; border-color: rgb(170, 166, 149); box-sizing: border-box;"><p class=""><span style="font-family: 站酷高端黑; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5;">TP53基因是一种肿瘤抑制基因，是迄今发现的与人类肿瘤相关性最高，也是被研究得最多的基因。由于TP53基因有防止正常细胞变成癌细胞的重要作用，因此也被称作“基因卫士”。</span></p><p class=""><br></p><p class=""><span style="font-family: 站酷高端黑; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5;">然</span><span style="font-family: 站酷高端黑; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5;">而，TP53基因的突变（缺失）与肿瘤的发生、发展有着密切的关系，75%的癌症患者都存在TP53基因突变。</span><span style="font-family: 站酷高端黑; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5;">一项涵盖12个肿瘤类型，共计3281例肿瘤的检测发现，TP53的平均突变频率较高约为42%。中国人群中，TP53异常者约占22%。研究证实，该基因如果发生突变，肿瘤往往更具侵袭性，</span><span style="font-family: 站酷高端黑; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5;">预后较差。</span></p></section></section></section></section><section class="" data-tools="135编辑器" data-id="90143" style="border: 0px none; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align:center;"><section style="display: inline-block; vertical-align: middle; padding-right: 3px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="border-top-width: 3px; border-top-style: solid; border-top-color: transparent; border-left-width: 3px; border-left-style: solid; border-left-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); float: right; box-sizing: border-box;"></section><section style="; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 1em; margin-right: 3px; padding: 0.5em; background: rgb(128, 177, 53);transform: rotate(360deg);-webkit-transform: rotate(360deg);-moz-transform: rotate(360deg);-ms-transform: rotate(360deg);-o-transform: rotate(360deg);"><p class="" data-original-title="" title="">2</p></section><section style="border-bottom-width: 3px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: transparent; border-left-width: 3px; border-left-style: solid; border-left-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); margin-top: -3px; float: right; box-sizing: border-box;"></section></section><section style="display: inline-block; vertical-align: middle; margin-left: -3em; font-size: 0.875em; line-height: 1.5; padding: 0.5em 1em 0.5em 3em; box-sizing: border-box; background: rgb(238, 238, 238);"><p class="" data-brushtype="text">项目意义</p></section></section></section><p><br></p><p class="" style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 站酷高端黑; font-size: 14px;">基因检测是目前最有效与最先进的肿瘤筛查方法，从分子水平评估患癌风险，破译个体抗癌能力。</span><span style="font-family: 站酷高端黑; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit;">通过TP53抑癌基因检测，寻找基因发生突变的位点，从而对个体的患病风险进行有效的</span><span style="font-family: 站酷高端黑; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit;">预警。</span></p>
